desc: Buy algae and everything you need to grow it at UTEX. Identification, DNA sequencing, and biochemical analysis are just a few services available. UTEX is a Non-Profit whose principle financial support is obtained through the NSF, University of Texas at Austin, and through the sale of cultures to the research community.

layout.text: BG-11(-N) Now Available! | Easy-to-prepare Media Kits for large volumes of media. Add-In components for specific nutrient boosts and upgrade kits to build upon simple base media.
